{"word":"H6944 - קֹדֶשׁ - qôdesh - ko'-desh - Consecrated","slug":"H6944","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">קֹדֶשׁ</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Transliteration: </strong>qôdesh"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Phonetic: </strong>ko'-desh"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Short Definition: </strong>Consecrated"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>&#x05E7;&#x05D3;&#x05E9;&#x05C1; - qo&#x0302;desh</b> - <i>ko'-desh</i><p/>From <a href=\"#/H6942\">H6942</a>; a <i>sacred</i> place or thing; rarely abstractly <i>sanctity: - </i>consecrated (thing), dedicated (thing), hallowed (thing), holiness, (X most) holy (X day, portion, thing), saint, sanctuary."},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/H4720\">H4720</a>, <a href=\"#/H6918\">H6918</a>, <a href=\"#/H6942\">H6942</a>, <a href=\"#/H6943\">H6943</a>, <a href=\"#/H6945\">H6945</a>, <a href=\"#/H6946\">H6946</a>, <a href=\"#/H6947\">H6947</a>, <a href=\"#/H6948\">H6948</a>"}]}